{"tid":1610673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2/10 全民憤怒日","createTime":"2019-10-01T18:58:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T11:38:14.000Z","uid":261118,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d83d89fb4438881d0bbef6e97897cb5377e5354a","tid":1610673,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:58:22.000Z","msg":"經過1/10，好多人今晚都瞓唔著/受傷，有義士被近距離開實彈謀殺，加上又有百幾個手足被捕，相信大家都好憤怒同擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我喺度請求大家，聽日停止開喇叭播「肥媽有話兒」同埋「有班警察毅進仔」一日，因為我笑唔出，亦都唔想見到大家嘻皮笑臉係度唱同笑！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解？有手足心囗中左實彈受重傷，仲要被告暴動！仲有百幾個手足係黑警手上生死未卜！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以玩少一日！笑少一日！保持心中既一團怒火！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為左中槍同被捕既手足，可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你食屎喇，我要撚狗，唔可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28ba595a88c8cecbe9ac0b436f2bd2f6c8be77a6","tid":1610673,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:06:31.000Z","msg":"幫我推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5adda0ea26f8bb75121ffaf3addfb84575fcf2b","tid":1610673,"uid":15133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:11:34.000Z","msg":"提唔起勁 唔知點笑"},{"pid":"7106bfd23698f82e3adc6aff56186d2f52e09c7d","tid":1610673,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b5adda0ea26f8bb75121ffaf3addfb84575fcf2b","tid":1610673,"uid":15133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:11:34.000Z","msg":"提唔起勁 唔知點笑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:12:28.000Z","msg":"幫我推上去比大家知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14bcc8d4872888e0eb1b952ab888878593bb20e4","tid":1610673,"uid":24984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T19:19:25.